00:01:31.533 --> 00:01:33.867 align:middle line:90%,end
<c.magenta>一个域名 与你网站的域名相同</c>

00:01:33.933 --> 00:01:35.567 align:middle line:90%,end
<c.magenta>以及一个资源的路径</c>

00:01:37.267 --> 00:01:38.833 align:middle line:90%,end
<c.magenta>要添加深度链接</c>

00:01:38.900 --> 00:01:42.467 align:middle line:90%,end
